Class RateSheet

  • java.lang.Object
    • Objects.RateSheet

  • public class RateSheet
extends java.lang.Object
    Use this class for defining the rates of the companies. This is the rate of the merchandise that is charged to the store for the cost of the transportation. There is also a minimum value for the rate for what the charge will be for the company no matter what
    Since:
    2/25/2021
